name: 2D Visualization 图表组件
description:
Content Introduction


The large screen data visualization 2D component is designed by RayData Lab. We hope to help designers quickly and easily complete the visualization of 2D prototypes, and welcome more like-minded partners to join us.


The design styles in this version of the component are derived from RayData Pro, welcome to register to experience it. If you have any questions, please contact us at yuzhen.xue@raykite.com
